your database is in the cluster,

00:42:09.400 --> 00:42:10.940
which means it's orchestrated by the cluster.

00:42:11.700 --> 00:42:12.940
If you don't give it any limits

00:42:13.580 --> 00:42:15.800
and you're running multiples and you do a backup,

00:42:16.400 --> 00:42:18.460
the resources when you do a backup go up.

00:42:21.939 --> 00:42:22.660
Yes, 100%.

